<Package Name="TUI" xmlns="http://opentap.io/schemas/package" Version="$(GitVersion)" OS="Windows,Linux">
  <Description>
The OpenTAP TUI is a textual based user interface that can be used from a terminal. It gives you a graphical way to create OpenTAP test plans (.TapPlan). As well, as editing OpenTAP settings.

It supports running in almost every terminal including in Docker containers.

